      <body>
        <div xml:id="song30">
          <head rend="italic">Youth and Beauty.</head>
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
          <div type="underlay">
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l>THou art so fair, and yong withall,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">thou kindl'st yong desires in me,</l>
            <l>restoreing life to leaves that fall,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">and sight to Eyes that hardly see,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">halfe those fresh Beauties bloom in thee.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
        <div>
            <lg type="stanza">
              <l>Those under sev'rall Hearbs and Flowr's,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">Disguis'd, were all <hi rend="italic">Medea</hi> gave,</l>
              <l>When she recal'd Times flying howrs,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">And aged <hi rend="italic">Ã†son</hi> from his grave,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">For Beauty can both kill and save.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="stanza">
              <l>Youth it enflames, but age it cheers,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">I would go back, but not return,</l>
              <l>To twenty but to twice those yeers;</l>
              <l rend="indent1">Not blaze, but ever constant burn,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">For fear my Cradle prove my Urn.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
        </div>
